Terrific staff with strong, neighborhood atmosphere. We often reserve the room in the back for meetings in the mornings. They have a wide variety of low cost items like bagels, oatmeal, muffins to balance a budget. Great selection of pizzas, sandwiches and salads at lunch.  We also stop by here for dessert and coffee with quiet conversation after having a more formal evening meal. Patio is a great to enjoy the weather when the evening is pleasant. Locally and family owned.

